{"tid":384733,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】Hori RAP.N開箱+主線之龍 Day105 2/9 【人中之龍6】","createTime":"2017-09-02T14:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T01:49:20.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d5929fb14425b1e9da263119e2237b01b7d0868","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=zdDDyw%2BdQtyF7U1PSVLwbAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5687d07b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=zdDDyw%2BdQtyF7U1PSVLwbAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ed1cba8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=zdDDyw%2BdQtyF7U1PSVLwbAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=509b1fc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"126628500a70ef195a5f349c26105de261324334","tid":384733,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"861af72fbae111dbdad977530e961065d5b692fb","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b349aca2ea7e8b1f1323ce824c9ac61ae7fb5134","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b7e182237c864811ceea84c6c5f2f86d292054","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8067d62da45cdb3a7ba3d5aa3d52d3737859e47","tid":384733,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:07:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a7a3c79fa6eacda5c4072d4e5a7c8ca399c37d0","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e1c2cf317f46c78bf5154747315c3769efd09a","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86c56f271ad61c997f2c6af77551aa769a9a1dd","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aec9ca9d198aad612d67d7139ef012f8f9448c0","tid":384733,"uid":122942,"like":0,"